<h2><a name="keepalive">KeepAlive</a></h2>
<strong>Syntax: (Apache 1.1)</strong> KeepAlive <em>max-requests</em><br>
<strong>Default: (Apache 1.1)</strong> <code>KeepAlive 5</code><br>
